<div class="content-box">
    <h3>Important Information</h3>
    <p>
        Welcome to the official website of Madhya Pradesh Employees Selection Board (MPESB).
        This portal provides information about various recruitment examinations, admit cards,
        results, and other important notifications.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="content-box">
    <h3>About MPESB</h3>
    <p>
        The Madhya Pradesh Employees Selection Board (Madhya Pradesh Karmchari Chayan Mandal)
        is a state government organization responsible for conducting recruitment examinations
        for various government departments in Madhya Pradesh.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="content-box">
    <h3>Our Services</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">We provide the following services:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 20px; line-height: 2;">
        <li>Conducting competitive examinations for Group A, B, C, and D posts</li>
        <li>Publishing recruitment notifications and advertisements</li>
        <li>Issuing admit cards for registered candidates</li>
        <li>Declaring examination results and merit lists</li>
        <li>Providing online application facilities</li>
    </ul>
</div>
